interesting points: The event was during nighttime and conditions were mostly clear., Thousands of people in the area witnessed the phenomenon., Witnesses described the object appearing on fire while visibly traveling through the atmosphere., The object was reported to have burned up completely upon its disappearance., The report emphasizes a need for confidentiality regarding witness identities.
witness description: The report mentions witnesses but does not provide specific descriptions.
